headline: A Changing of the Guard: Powell Out, Hassett Favored
summary: As Jerome Powell's tenure enters its final phase, markets are looking ahead to the next chapter of monetary policy leadership. Trump ally and "dove" Kevin Hassett is the overwhelming favorite to replace Powell.

headline: Millrose Properties, Inc. Comments on Completion of Lennar Exchange Offer
summary: MIAMI, December 01, 2025--Millrose Properties, Inc. (NYSE: MRP) ("Millrose" or the "Company") today issued the following statement in connection with the completion of Lennar Corporation's (NYSE: LEN and LEN.B) ("Lennar") previously disclosed offer to exchange shares of Millrose Class A common stock for shares of Lennar Class A common stock.

headline: 1 S&P 500 Stock to Target This Week and 2 We Ignore
